---
title: Sesame Crusted Chicken & Soy-Garlic Pumpkin with Spinach Slaw & Yuzu Mayonnaise
description: Keep chicken strips tender and tasty with an easy sesame coating – just toss it in a quick mix and you’re done!
With a crisp spinach slaw, roasted soy-garlic pumpkin and zingy yuzu mayo, this family delight combines
colours and textures for a delicious feast!

 *This recipe is under 650kcal per serving.*
